{"tid":1882048,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"木村拓哉曬照為武漢疫情祈禱　粉絲點破「這口罩沒有用」","createTime":"2020-02-16T03:54:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-16T03:59:53.000Z","uid":212731,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7e2c0f32a83138364f961dc50e584361cc24f46b","tid":1882048,"uid":212731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T03:54:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200210/UICQL55KFMB2YJIHW4PH6KYUXI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200210%2FUICQL55KFMB2YJIHW4PH6KYUXI%2F&d=sh6QB3P1ZXxG4EHsBexfbm%2Fv5hJrJLSiIP9i8i%2FMgDc%3D&h=65c600d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200210%2FUICQL55KFMB2YJIHW4PH6KYUXI%2F&h=45b3b62a\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200210/UICQL55KFMB2YJIHW4PH6KYUXI/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GgDBief.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGgDBief.jpg&h=92895b23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n武漢肺炎疫情蔓延，眾多藝人除了捐款、捐口罩外也齊聲為疫情祈禱，47歲「日劇天王」木村拓哉今也在微博發文為粉絲加油打氣，並曬出戴口罩的自拍，反倒被網友提醒他的口罩沒有防疫作用。<br />\n <br />\n今木村拓哉在微博上發文寫道：「大家現在真的都非常辛苦，我們相互共渡難關吧。」從照片上可以看到木村戴上黑色口罩遮去大半臉，不過他所配戴的口罩只有防寒、防花粉功能，無法阻擋飛沫，不少網友見到照片後，紛紛替木村拓哉擔心，留言提醒「你這個口罩沒有用」、「這個口罩不能防病毒啊，只能防一下花粉」、「日本也有不少病例了，也要注意保護自己呀」、「哥你要戴N95口罩才比較管用的啊」。（鄭維蓁／綜合報導）"},{"pid":"529c494d7e4100bea5921d6bc25c406aa452cd15","tid":1882048,"uid":212731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T03:55:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gGAv676.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgGAv676.jpg&h=ad1e6073&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d43388f0a8463d9b3808cb60bf95c3b573f10365","tid":1882048,"uid":339272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T03:59:53.000Z","msg":"條鏈好金"}]}